WRITING.TITLE: My strategy to survive 15 turns, 3bp assassin day
WRITING.TEXT: Hi, it's my first guide so if you have any critic feel free to comment First off with team composition: https://imgur.com/KxUbgjH Note: Support waver need to have his skill at least 6/6/6. I run this with Chaldea combat uniform lv 6 You can have cu with volumen hydrargyrum 5*(gacha) for extra 3 turn invincible, summer precognition 4* (garden of sinner ce) or parted sea 3* (fp gacha) for 1 hit evade, or simply carp ce for more damage This strategy is not perfect, it's quite time consuming but I have won without using any command seal. Start Battle 1: Turn 1: start with 40 star, Use waver 1st skill on Shiki Try to charge your np as much as possible, DO NOT kill all the mobs in one turn Battle 2: Normally you will start this at turn 3 of the fight Turn 1-2/15: Use all waver buff on turn 1, try to get everyone's np to 100% Turn 3/15: Eli buster buff, shiki art buff, master attack buff, you can reset if waver can't stun, use Eli skill to change rng, you should get at least 1.5 mil damage, and both hands die here Turn 4: Switch Eli with George, use taunt, again, reset if geogre die from crit, try getting ibaraki to hit George twice, use Geogre skill to change rng. Turn 5: if you haven't had to use George guts to change rng, use it now, he's should die this turn and gut up again Turn 6: ibaraki np, George die, Mash in Note: try your best to charge shiki np and keep her alive Turn 7: stun ibaraki with master spell Turn 8: waver cooldown is done,buff your team again plus mash def up Turn 9: keep mash alive to taunt the next ibaraki np, fire off shiki np if she had it Turn 10: ibaraki np, Mash taunt, Mash die, Eli in Turn 11-13: with Eli, waver, shiki, hold your ground until cu comes in Turn 14-15: full health cu with 3 evade and gut can survive this That's it for my guide, hope it can help, thank you for reading.
